OL,7,FBy the age of 19, I was an alcoholic.
OL,8,FMy life soon spiralled into a seven-
OL,9,Fyear battle that caused unimaginable
OL,10,Fhurt to my family. Seven years of me
OL,11,Ftrying to shout louder than the
OL,12,Faddictive voice in my head telling me
OL,13,Fthat I "could drink like a normal
OL,14,Fperson". The truth was, I couldn't,
OL,15,Fand I will never be able to.
