OL,7,FThe thing that I initially thought was
OL,8,Fmy saviour, ended up ripping my life
OL,9,Fto pieces. It consumed what were
OL,10,Fsupposed to be the best years of my
OL,11,Flife and made me feel like I was
OL,12,Fworthless.
OL,14,FI spent six months in rehab, lost
OL,15,Fseveral jobs, destroyed relationships
OL,16,Fand eventually ended up with alcoholic
OL,17,Fliver disease all before my 26th
OL,18,Fbirthday.
