OL,7,FI've been travelling around the
OL,8,Fcountry for ITV's Tonight Programme to
OL,9,Ffind out why, and more importantly,
OL,10,Fhow people are putting down the pints.
OL,12,FFirst up was Liverpool to meet a group
OL,13,Fof students who have been leading the
OL,14,Fcharge. Surprisingly, the sober
OL,15,Fmovement is being led by young people.
