OL,7,FThe rise in no and low alcoholic
OL,8,Fdrinks has also been helping some
OL,9,Fpeople curb their drinking and could
OL,10,Falso play its part in reducing alcohol
OL,11,Fharm. The IWSR (International Wines
OL,12,Fand Spirits Record) forecast the
OL,13,Findustry to grow at 7% over the next
OL,14,Ffive years. But question marks remain
OL,15,Fover how accessible the products are
OL,16,Fto everyone.
OL,18,FJohn Holmes, Professor of Alcohol
OL,19,FPolicy at the University of Sheffield,
OL,20,Fhas been leading a study on the impact
OL,21,Fof no and low drinks on the UK.
