OL,7,FMy liver, which was on brink of
OL,8,Fcirrhosis a decade ago, has completely
OL,9,Frecovered. I can't quite believe how
OL,10,Ffortunate I am to have made such a
OL,11,Fgreat recovery. I know for many people
OL,12,Fin a similar position the outcome can
OL,13,Fbe far worse.
OL,15,FI don't want anyone to go through the
OL,16,Fhell that alcohol put me and my family
OL,17,Fthrough. So, knowing that there is a
OL,18,Fgrowing sober movement and that
OL,19,Fattitudes towards alcohol are
OL,20,Fchanging, fills me with optimism.
